<li><a href="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Industrial_Society_and_Its_Future" class="extiw" title="s:Industrial Society and Its Future">Industrial Society and Its Future (The Unabomber's Manifesto)</a></li>
<li><sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span title="&#160;since October 2012" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="Wikipedia_Link_rot" title="Wikipedia:Link rot">dead link</a></i>]</span></sup><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.insurgentdesire.org.uk">Insurgent Desire (collection of Neo-Luddite/Green Anarchist essays)</a></li>
