<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.nature.com/news/2011/220811/full/476373a.html"><i>Stand up against the anti-technology terrorists</i> by Gerardo Herrera Corral, Nature 476, 373 (2011)</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.technologydependencereduction.com/">Technology Dependence Reduction - <i>Reducing dependence on technology and overcoming information overload.</i></a></li>
